Yes — for 200-extras, I would treat these as scratchpad optional %post snippets, not normal required Kickstart building blocks yet.

Use them only when intentionally included in a future developer-workstation.ks.j2 or custom override. I would not include any of these in minimal or small-disk templates by default.

Important: the files below are self-contained %post sections. Include them near the end of a Kickstart template, not inside another %post block.

